&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead by Example:&lt;/strong&gt; Provide high-quality, evidence-based patient care, setting the clinical standard for your team and acting as a model for Tia’s care philosophy.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Master Clinical Quality:&lt;/strong&gt; Own clinical outcomes and documentation consistency within your clinic, ensuring your team delivers care that is both high-touch and high-quality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manage Complexity:&lt;/strong&gt; Act as the clinical point person for complex patient cases or team issues, utilizing sound judgment and professionalism to resolve challenges in real-time.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
