&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Care Model Support:&lt;/strong&gt; Contribute to the ongoing iteration of Tia’s care model through technology development, interdisciplinary case studies, protocol development, clinical content review, and innovation.&lt;/li&gt;
