&lt;p data-start=&quot;185&quot; data-end=&quot;384&quot;&gt;We’re hiring experienced Nurse Practitioners and Physician Assistants to provide on-call/per diem coverage across Tia’s Eastside Los Angeles clinics, including Pasadena, Silver Lake, and Studio City.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;386&quot; data-end=&quot;758&quot;&gt;This is a high-autonomy role for clinicians who can step into a clinic, quickly integrate into the flow, and deliver high-quality, whole-person care from day one. You’ll support continuity of care during same-day callouts, high-volume periods, and planned coverage gaps, ensuring patients receive timely, thoughtful, clinically excellent care no matter where they’re seen.&lt;/p&gt;
