&lt;p&gt;This role offers the opportunity to provide direct patient care while also engaging in teaching, collaboration, and clinical partnership across the organization. You’ll also have the unique opportunity to work with Tia’s technology teams, contributing feedback and insights that help shape the products and tools you use to care for patients.&lt;/p&gt;
