&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working with data, reporting, and systems to drive better decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Highly detail-oriented, organized, and accountable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to operate both strategically and tactically in a fast-moving environment&lt;/li&gt;
